# Proxy pool — one proxy URL per line. Copy to `proxy.txt` and fill in.
# Used ONLY for the Loop/Cantonloop wallet auth + deposit path (datacenter IPs
# get 403 there). Trading (orders/balances) runs direct, no proxy.
#
# The bot tries each proxy in turn until one authenticates, so list several
# residential proxies for reliability. Blank lines and `#` comments are ignored.
#
# NEVER commit proxy.txt — it holds credentials and this repo is public.
#
# Format: scheme://user:pass@host:port   (http/https/socks5 supported by undici)
#
# http://user:pass@residential1.example.com:8080
# http://user:pass@residential2.example.com:8080
# socks5://user:pass@residential3.example.com:1080
